name: Super Thin Wireless Bluetooth Keyboard for iPad/iPhone 4.0 OS/PC/Smartphone/HTPC
description:
Super Thin Wireless Bluetooth Keyboard for iPad/iPhone 4.0 OS/PC/Smartphone/HTPC

A Bluetooth keyboard will set you free from the hassles of typing directly into your iPad and Smartphone devices. 

Compact, lightweight, and easy-to-use, a wireless bluetooth keyboard will allow you to get full control over your iPad and mobile phones. 

With a bluetoth keyboard, typing long emails, reports, and other business files will never be as painful and strenuous as it used to be.

It’s cable-free, so you’re free to type wherever you like — with the keyboard in front of your computer or even on your lap.

Bluetooth Version: Bluetooth V2.1

78 key design, with 12 multi-function keys

Scissor-switch keypad design, confortable and ergonomic design

Built-in intelligent power manage software for power 
conservation

Built-in software solution with Bluetooth human interface device and comply with the standard version of the Blurtooth SIG 

Bluetooth 2.1

Powered by 2pcs AAA battery (not included)
Working range: 10M

iPad, Mac OS
Windows OS(Windows XP, Windows Vista, Windows7)

iPad/ iPhone 4.0 OS/ PC/ Smartphone/ HTPC
